item.title: maraiah connection
item.description: 5:00am CST Thursday 31 October 2002 Recently Maraiah sent me a reverse survey, where we tell what we know about the other person. I don't know a lot about her really, but for the record, this is what I wrote: Re: Survey with a twist HOW WELL DO YOU KNOW ME? Fill in the blanks about ME and send it back. BUT FIRST, send a blank one out to all your friends so they can return the favor for you.
